Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果我不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要好好练习 成为优秀的正式领航员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么 怎么了吗 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说如果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说如果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被逮捕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的早晨非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是今天 凉快得让人神清气爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 本应像平时一样进行三人的共同练习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这个这么美好的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不知不觉挺直肩背 干劲满满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 腋下没用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈姿势不好看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪完头发一周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都觉得 有点变成熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级翘头发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还没有的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是长头发的时候没发现的短发的弊端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 头发变短了 觉得脖子有点凉凉的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.82,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 爱哭鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要静养一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是热感冒 但即使退烧了也不能大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经联系过你外出的父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给灯里和爱丽丝打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你明天开始暂时不能参加共同练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的练习 那两个人没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又睡了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然到晚上会好一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一连睡上三天 就会觉得时间变得好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 无聊无聊无聊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天到晚都在睡 现在完全睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书和杂志又都看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我就要得无聊病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事情 有没有有趣的事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃布丁哦 涂了奶油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出去的话 会不会被晃前辈骂呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的客人给我们送来了感谢信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出逃成功～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比起看杂志更能提神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像在度假一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔感冒一下也不是坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家咖啡厅的卡布奇诺非常出名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以下船品尝 需要去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上在酒店已经吃过卡布奇诺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕胖 还是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}是吗 Espresso也是这里的名品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点像在冒险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来看你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我见不了你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对禁止入内哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说绝对禁止入内啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎么了嘛 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还在为剪短头发而…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是布丁的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是布丁害我变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧第三天的我无聊得实在不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上又已经退烧 没什么大碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就偷偷跑出来 买买东西 吃吃卡布奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始有点冒险的感觉 很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错 我不在也没有偷懒 在好好练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}要换个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就算我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}那我们到那边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也还是一切照旧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时侯 我开始觉得很别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我应该存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说理所当然的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅相隔几米的灯里那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却好像是被透明的墙壁所阻隔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常遥远的 另外一个空间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然变得害怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从那个地方逃开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去 我要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须尽快回到那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我回过神来 就不知道为什么开始哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哭成那样像傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般 难得你们好心来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过给我回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要大睡特睡一场 彻底告别感冒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回我可是认真的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是之前都不认真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 最后你买到布丁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没买到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这事彻底忘掉跑回来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是探病的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还涂了奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让她们看到了我爱哭鬼的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她们来看我 我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔感冒一下也不坏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁冒出这种傻傻的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个夏日的尾声中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后过了两天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感冒已经完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈今天不用上学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午我们三个人会进行惯例的共同练习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得把感冒没能练习的几天都补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然…决心要补回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 蓝华 禁止啊禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止啊 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:14.12,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那颗 少女心啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 还差一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止啊禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自己说有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实还算是比较可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比这两个要好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死性子的小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不注意马上就变成一张臭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导游词也变成念经
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆呆的灯里也是 一不注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}练习中好美禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美模式全开 一个劲地东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这样还能维持住共同练习也算是一种奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是多亏了我紧紧地握住了缰绳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我也…变得漫不经心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的冲动从早上开始就纠缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 那个发夹好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 超级适合现在的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 好了 接下来到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 蓝华 禁止啊禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得给这两人做榜样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要把练习好好坚持到最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾莉西亚前辈 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您现在要去迎接客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 好可爱的发夹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎怎么了啊 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是比感冒还要严重的疾病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是发夹不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪这个发夹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我的心从早上开始就七上八下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个发夹很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的东西当然可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我剪了短头发以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没见过阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 短发的新造型还没让阿鲁看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早换上这个发夹后 突然就想让阿鲁看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这么重要的事情怎么不跟我们说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难找到见面的机会啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪头发又过了这么长时间了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个发夹就是很好的机会啊 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级快去见他的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在开始就算蓝华是进行个人练习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…承你们贵言…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里要好好看着小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她摆臭脸 导游词像念经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小后辈要看着灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她集中精神练习 别东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…然 然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想让阿鲁看看自己的新发型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在…期待什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力调节员的工作场所 我在中学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在社会课的参观中来过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叫重力石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像糖果一样 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西居然能控制AQUA的重力 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁的工作场所好像是在这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是…阿鲁的上司…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像叫…阿帕爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个领航员…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姬屋的蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 阿鲁的朋友蓝华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发剪短了一下子没认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我刚好到这附近就过来看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到这种地方的附近还真是稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个 阿鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁吗 虽然有点早 不过他去吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他今天上夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层新开了一家乌冬店 他去那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那里的阿龟乌冬很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}注：加入鱼糕 蘑菇 豆腐皮等材料的什锦乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿龟乌冬…总觉得有点老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了见阿鲁特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我没什么特别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是我带来的布丁 涂奶油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底来做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁的话肯定会说消化消化 然后走楼梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…在期待什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐 你怎么在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我刚好到这附近啦 所以过来看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有在想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁吃完阿龟乌冬要走楼梯来消化…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我去吃阿龟乌冬了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿帕爷爷告诉我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐 你把头发剪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短头发也很适合你呢 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了听这句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天…我为什么要这么烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我一点都不明白自己到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我却觉得有点高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了 点心已经给阿帕爷爷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个发夹也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你上去吧 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许是小小的发夹带来的魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 没有影子的召唤者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:47.35,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:02:00.33,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:15.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:28.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:34.50,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:42.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:49.59,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:59.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:47.35,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:02:00.33,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:15.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:28.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:34.50,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:42.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:49.59,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:59.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:23:00.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}去りゆく夏の日 思いを寄せて集うバルコニー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:17.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水面にきらめく風のゴンドラ いま滑り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:31.80,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}流れる時の河でめぐり逢えた人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:42.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いま夜空を焦がして輝く夏の夜の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:53.04,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}忘れないでSmile Again いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:23:00.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}即将逝去的夏日 怀抱着思念来到露台上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:17.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在水面上闪耀着 那风之凤尾舟 正要启航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:31.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不断流逝的时间长河中 人们彼此邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:42.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}划过长夜之空的是那炫目的夏夜之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:53.04,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}请不要忘记Smile Again 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【INJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:08.98,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもどおりの朝 きらめいて見える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:20.43,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}気がついたの いつだってあなたがいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:31.04,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}短く切った髪に選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:40.71,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}キラリ ちいさなお気に入りのピンで
